-- P0-7 regression: an un-annotated (Num-polymorphic) self-tail-recursive loop.
-- Its recursive call lowers to a `CDict` head (the dict-pass widens the callee with
-- a leading Num dict param), which historically stayed a plain `call` + `return` on
-- wasm — growing the stack and overflowing V8.  The recursive self-call MUST now be a
-- `return_call` (constant stack); N=1_000_000 would overflow a plain-call stack.
-- (No signature on purpose: the annotated monomorphic path already tail-called.)
polyLoop acc n = if n == 0 then acc else polyLoop (acc + n) (n - 1)
main = println (polyLoop 0 1000000)
